SURAT PAULUS KEPADA

THE EPISTLE OF PAUL

JEMAAT DI FILIPI

TO THE PHILIPPIANS

 

 

Penulis: Paulus dengan Timotius, hamba-hamba Kristus Yesus (1:1).

Author: Paul with Timothy, slaves of Christ Jesus (1:1).

 

 

Waktu Penulisan: Kira-kira 64 M, mungkin setelah Surat Efesus ditulis (cf. 1:25; 2:24).

Time of Writing: Approximately A.D. 64, perhaps after Ephesians was written (cf. 1:25; 2:24).

 

 

Tempat penulisan: Sebuah penjara di Roma (1:13; Kis. 28:30).

Place of Writing: Rome, where Paul was imprisoned (1:13; Acts 28:30).

 

 

Penerima: Orang-orang kudus di Filipi, bersama penilik dan diaken (1:1).

Recipients: The saints in Philippi, with the overseers and deacons (1:1).

 

 

Pokok: Mengalami Kristus - Mengambil Kristus sebagai Hidup, Pola, Sasaran, Kuasa, dan Rahasia Kita

Subject of Philippians: Experiencing Christ�Taking Christ as Our Living, Pattern, Goal, Power, and Secret
